Barrick Says Zaldivar Mine Normal After Chile Power Outage

-- B y   H e l e n   M u r p h y
-- 
2011-06-19T21:17:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-19/barrick-says-zaldivar-mine-normal-after-chile-power-outage.html
Activity at  Barrick Gold Corp. (ABX) ’s
Zaldivar copper mine was “normal” after  Chile ’s northern
electricity grid was knocked out, said Scott Brubacher,
Barrick’s corporate communications director.  Daily El Mercurio de Antofagasta said this morning BHP
Billiton Ltd.’s Escondida and Zaldivar mines suffered
electricity cuts. Brubacher didn’t provide further details in an
e-mailed response to questions.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Helen Murphy in Bogota at 
 hmurphy1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 